\f0\fs54 \cf2 Beef with Broccoli
\fs46 \
\
2 tbsp. vegetable oil, divided\
3/4 lb. beef sirloin (center cut) steak, boneless, sliced into bite-size pieces\
3 cloves garlic, finely chopped\
1 shallot, finely chopped\
4 cups broccoli florets (about 2 small crowns)\
2 tbsp. cornstarch\
3/4 cup water\
1.3 cup soy sauce\
2 tbsp. brown sugar\
1 tsp. ground ginger\
1/8 tsp. crushed red pepper flakes\
optional: cooked white rice\
\
